text: This Is My Country () is a 1984 Filipino French drama movie directed by Lino Brocka and starring Phillip Salvador, Gina Alajar, Carmi Martin, Claudia Zobel, Raoul Aragon, Paquito Diaz, Rez Cortez, and Lucita Soriano. ==Other websites== * Category:1984 drama movies Category:Filipino movies Category:French drama movies Category:Movies directed by Lino Brocka
title: This Is My Country (movie)
